Usage: cmus [OPTION]...
Curses based music player.

      --listen ADDR   listen on ADDR instead of $CMUS_SOCKET or $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/cmus-socket
                      ADDR is either a UNIX socket or host[:port]
                      WARNING: using TCP/IP is insecure!
      --plugins       list available plugins and exit
      --show-cursor   always visible cursor
      --help          display this help and exit
      --version       v2.7.1

Use cmus-remote to control cmus from command line.
Report bugs to <cmus-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>.
